# Change summary format

When you finish a fix or feature, reply with **two sections only**:

## What changed

- **Bullets** — one change per line, **≤10 words** when possible (stretch only if needed).
- No long prose, no architecture essays, no duplicate bullets.

## How to verify

- **Bullets** — concrete steps **I** take locally (commands, URLs, clicks).
- Short imperatives: “Run X”, “Open Y”, “Expect Z”.
- Skip obvious fluff (“save files”, “restart computer”).

If nothing to test, one bullet: **No manual test steps.**
